 argument  1 = urea.nw
 


============================== echo of input deck ==============================
start urea
title "urea opt+freq (B3LYP/6-31g*)"
echo

geometry units angstrom
  C  0.000000  0.000000  0.000000
  O  1.210000  0.000000  0.000000
  N  -0.640000  1.110000  0.000000
  N  -0.640000  -1.110000  0.000000
  H  -1.520000  1.140000  0.810000
